description: (Submitted for US, Canada only) Passionate about the news? Get in-depth insight and analysis into the most significant issues of the day with NEWSWEEK’s opinion-leading editorial from the most influential names in journalism. You can also customize your news experience by adding feeds from all of your favorite news outlets. Only from NEWSWEEK. Only on your Palm. Do you NEWSWEEK?
versionNote: Newsweek domestic (US & Canada) application submission, changes made based on feedback from Palm (doc AppReview_newsweek_v090)
